data.description: Nestled in the heart of St. Pete Beach, this exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning 2,812 square feet is a waterfront haven that's been masterfully renovated. Situated on an impressive nearly 100-foot waterfront lot, the property boasts awe-inspiring, unobstructed water views, treating you to breathtaking sunrises and sunsets daily. The home's modern elegance is highlighted by its impact windows and doors, providing both energy efficiency and storm protection. The location is truly unbeatable, offering the perfect blend of serenity and convenience with just a short stroll to the pristine beach. Outdoor enthusiasts will relish in the backyard's boating amenities, including a boat lift and jet ski lift, making water adventures easily accessible. As a bonus, nature enthusiasts will find solace in the regular visits of dolphins and manatees, creating a unique and enchanting waterfront experience right from your backyard. Whether you seek a peaceful retreat or an entertainer's paradise, this property presents endless possibilities for crafting your dream coastal lifestyle. Don't let this opportunity for quintessential St. Pete Beach living pass you by – schedule your private showing today and be prepared to fall in love with waterfront living at its finest.
